column2: Qutoutiao, Inc. operates as an online platform for headlines. The company is headquartered in Shanghai, Shanghai and currently employs 1,865 full-time employees. The firm is a mobile content aggregator and its main mobile application is called Qutotiao, through which the Company can provide personalized content, such as, articles and short videos, to users.
11f Bldg 3 Xingchuang Technology Plz, 5005 Nong, Shenjiang Rd
